{"id": 631, "genre": 1001, "title": "婚礼最可怕的部分是什么？", "description": "浑身的尴尬症都要发作了啦！", "record_count": 11291, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183501KZr2GliQpbSD8dwq.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-14T01:14:13Z", "options": [{"id": 24832, "content": "曾经很爱的人出现在自己面前 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304094}, {"id": 25089, "content": "随份子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305682}, {"id": 25604, "content": "逃婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308112}, {"id": 24838, "content": "为了热闹搞出来的低俗无聊的活动", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301018}, {"id": 25352, "content": "中西结合的各种违和感", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274779}, {"id": 33033, "content": "参加你爱过的人的婚礼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347847}, {"id": 25362, "content": "度蜜月前一天发现怀孕了，没法坐飞机，还要退机票！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 292004}, {"id": 24853, "content": "每一分每一秒", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285082}, {"id": 24856, "content": "新郎哭了 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304355}, {"id": 24857, "content": "司仪普通话不标准", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304356}, {"id": 24862, "content": "伴郎抢婚带走新郎。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304400}, {"id": 27935, "content": "婚姻是爱情的坟墓", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321385}, {"id": 27936, "content": "没有新娘", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321400}, {"id": 28962, "content": "全过程都像在表演 别人在看戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 328214}, {"id": 25635, "content": "仪式不结束不上主菜。司仪讲话的时候就怕宾客只顾闷头吃吃吃", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211828QPavyDp4UM7ltkYT.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142082}, {"id": 24868, "content": "当伴娘 知道新郎新娘各自恶心的婚前出轨的事 …\\", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289263}, {"id": 24869, "content": "听证婚人说一些爱党爱国的话，然后念结婚证把新人身份证号都念出来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269761}, {"id": 25381, "content": "婚宴开吃过程中司仪要唱一段", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307105}, {"id": 34855, "content": "婚礼就像看耍猴的，有意思吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134052}, {"id": 25128, "content": "最尴尬的事是：我们老家习俗摆酒不收人情.....纯亏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305920}, {"id": 24875, "content": "有钱就有真爱。", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211709qKtEobiyH0zTjPex.jpg", "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304314}, {"id": 24880, "content": "婚礼才不可怕，可怕的是以后的日子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301692}, {"id": 29489, "content": "婚后钱不放自个腰包。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330774}, {"id": 31793, "content": "还没开始宾客已经吃完走人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340417}, {"id": 24882, "content": "觉得整个婚礼媚俗不堪 特别想大喊一声别恶心了 可惜当时我还是孩子 最悲哀了", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187991}, {"id": 24884, "content": "你的挚爱跟别人结婚了，新郎不如你，而你还是一个单身狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301989}, {"id": 24885, "content": "伴娘太漂亮七大姑八大姨把伴娘认成新娘子", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304619}, {"id": 24886, "content": "新娘跑了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245029}, {"id": 25657, "content": "后悔结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308616}, {"id": 24890, "content": "不举", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239780}, {"id": 26176, "content": "煽情环节", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311566}, {"id": 28225, "content": "婚纱被伴娘踩掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323491}, {"id": 24904, "content": "站的那听司仪指挥。。。和机器人一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304720}, {"id": 100425, "content": "我无婚姻无关，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687277}, {"id": 24906, "content": "作为来宾，不知道婚礼进行到哪了，新郎新娘什么样子，只知道菜上到哪了", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 293428}, {"id": 26448, "content": "闹伴娘之类恶心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245196}, {"id": 25937, "content": "敬酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 182628}, {"id": 24915, "content": "牵过的狗被人牵走", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291459}, {"id": 25683, "content": "被长辈关怀的慰问：你啥时结啊？其实连对象都没有啊，啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308861}, {"id": 24920, "content": "我只想多吃点", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304856}, {"id": 25693, "content": "醒来了却是场梦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308914}, {"id": 24926, "content": "我去的时候我还没男朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304879}, {"id": 25440, "content": "和周围的人没话说。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305424}, {"id": 24929, "content": "所有人都教你该怎么做\n其实他们自己也狗屁不懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304934}, {"id": 31843, "content": "敬酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340866}, {"id": 39524, "content": "司仪疯狂煽情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 408655}, {"id": 26726, "content": "前男友或者前女友忽然出来 带走了新娘或者新郎", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 316835}, {"id": 24938, "content": "明明只是将就凑着过日子的却要假装好幸福好相爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270044}, {"id": 129386, "content": "看戏一样的，还是最俗套的演员和剧情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686424}, {"id": 25197, "content": "别人新娘恰好是自己初恋", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 303342}]}